      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUMPY BLUE (3) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (23.12) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. STOCK'S GIFT (6) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 3rd at this track over 400m. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and six minor placings to his credit. Can measure up. WONKY KEY DONKEY (4) box seated before sticking on well to finish one length away in second (22.89) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Overdue and gets her chance. DIVA'S DELIGHT (7) scored in dominant fashion last time. Sure to run well again.",
